doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title LawnAdmin

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap icons
        <!-- CSS only -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.8.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        
        

        // Google fonts
        link(rel='preconnect', href='https://fonts.gstatic.com')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,wght@0,600;1,600&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mulish:ital,wght@0,300;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top.shadow-sm
            .container.px-5
                a.navbar-brand.fw-bold(href='#page-top') LawnAdmin
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.bi-list
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.me-4.my-3.my-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.me-lg-3(href='#features') Features
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.me-lg-3(href='#download') Download
                    //- a.btn.btn-outline-light.py-3.px-4.rounded-pill(href='https://startbootstrap.com/theme/new-age', target='_blank') Download for free
                    a.btn.btn-primary.rounded-pill.px-3.mb-2.mb-lg-0(href='mailto:support@lawnadmin.com', target='_blank') 
                        span.d-flex.align-items-center
                            i.bi-chat-text-fill.me-2
                            span.small Send Feedback
                    

        // Mashead header
        header.masthead
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        // Mashead text and app badges
                        .mb-5.mb-lg-0.text-center.text-lg-start
                            h1.display-1.lh-1.mb-3 LawnAdmin
                            p.lead.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-5  Is dedicated to providing business management systems to landscape business owners so they have the ability to increase efficiency and grow their business.
                            .d-flex.flex-column.flex-lg-row.align-items-center
                                a.me-lg-3.mb-4.mb-lg-0(href='#!')
                                    img.app-badge(src='assets/img/google-play-badge.svg', alt='...')
                                a(href='#!')
                                    img.app-badge(src='assets/img/app-store-badge.svg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6
                        // Masthead device mockup feature
                        .masthead-device-mockup
                            include includes/gradient-circle
                            include includes/shape-1
                            include includes/shape-2
                            .device-wrapper
                                .device(data-device='iPhoneX', data-orientation='portrait', data-color='black')
                                    .screen.bg-black
                                        // PUT CONTENTS HERE:
                                        // * * This can be a video, image, or just about anything else.
                                        // * * Set the max width of your media to 100% and the height to
                                        // * * 100% like the demo example below.
                                        image <img src="assets\img\Use.webp" alt="App" style="width:100%;height:100%;">
                                        
                                        //- video(muted='muted', autoplay='', loop='', style='max-width: 100%; height: 100%;')
                                        //-     source(src='assets\img\Use.png', type='image/png')

        // Quote/testimonial aside
        aside.text-center.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-xl-8
                        .h2.fs-1.text-white.mb-4 “An intuitive solution designed for a prosperous industry becoming increasingly more reliant on technology!”
                        .h4.fw-normal.text-white.mb-4 - Bodner Brothers Landscaping
                 

        // App features section
        section#features
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-8.order-lg-1.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        .container-fluid.px-5
                            .row.gx-5
                                .col-md-6.mb-5
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-calendar-event.icon-feature
                                        h3.font-alt Google Calendar Integration
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Ensure all your jobs are scheduled with reminders and alerts so all employees can stay up to date!
                                .col-md-6.mb-5
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-receipt.icon-feature
                                        h3.font-alt Invoice Tracking 
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Decrease time spent on adding up past due invoices with LawnAdmin's customer outstanding balance tool
                            .row
                                .col-md-6.mb-5.mb-md-0
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-envelope.icon-feature
                                        h3.font-alt Email Invoices
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Increase productivity by customer email invoice notifications!
                                .col-md-6
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-wrench.icon-feature
                                        h3.font-alt Equipment Records
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Record equipment maintenance to keep your fleet running!
                    .col-lg-4.order-lg-0
                        // Features section device mockup
                        .features-device-mockup
                            include includes/gradient-circle
                            include includes/shape-1
                            include includes/shape-2
                            .device-wrapper
                                .device(data-device='iPhoneX', data-orientation='portrait', data-color='black')
                                    .screen.bg-black
                                        // PUT CONTENTS HERE:
                                        // * * This can be a video, image, or just about anything else.
                                        // * * Set the max width of your media to 100% and the height to
                                        // * * 100% like the demo example below.

                                        //insert use.png here
                                        
                                        image <img src="assets\img\Use2.webp" alt="App" style="width:100%;height:100%;">

        // Basic features section
        section.bg-light
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center.justify-content-center.justify-content-lg-between
                    .col-12.col-lg-5
                        h2.display-4.lh-1.mb-4 Enter a new age of landscaping
                        p.lead.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-5.mb-lg-0LawnAdmin LawnAdmin is a landscape business application that assists with essential administrative responsibilities by increasing internal efficiency through; email invoicing, estimate follow-ups, organized scheduling and equipment maintenance logs. Unlike Yardbook, this application is available as a mobile application or on the web. LawnAdmin users have a desire to reduce the amount of time spent on “tedious work” throughout the day, regarding administrative responsibilities. The owners of these small landscape businesses want to decrease the amount of time they spend completing the administrative activities of their business and more time addressing customer needs or growing their business. 
                    .col-sm-8.col-md-6
                        .px-5.px-sm-0
                        image <img src="assets\img\Usem2.webp" alt="App" style="width:130%;height:130%;padding-right:25%;">

        // Call to action section
        section.cta
            .cta-content
                .container.px-5
                    h2.text-white.display-1.lh-1.mb-4
                        |Get out of the office
                        br
                        |and on to the mower!
                    a.btn.btn-outline-light.py-3.px-4.rounded-pill(href='', target='_blank') Download for free

        // App badge section
        section#download.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary
            .container.px-5
                h2.text-center.text-white.font-alt.mb-4 Get the app now!
                .d-flex.flex-column.flex-lg-row.align-items-center.justify-content-center
                    a.me-lg-3.mb-4.mb-lg-0(href='#!')
                        img.app-badge(src='assets/img/google-play-badge.svg', alt='...')
                    a(href='#!')
                        img.app-badge(src='assets/img/app-store-badge.svg', alt='...')

        // Footer
        footer.bg-black.text-center.py-5
            .container.px-5
                .text-white-50.small
                    .mb-2 &copy; Lawn Admin 2022. All Rights Reserved.
                    a(href='#!') Privacy
                    span.mx-1 &middot;
                    a(href='#!') Terms
                    span.mx-1 &middot;
                    a(href='#!') FAQ
        
        include includes/feedback-modal.pug

